"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1930570-Rafael-Nadal-Carlos-Alcaraz-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Rafael NadalandCarlos Alcarazwere dumped out of the Olympics men's doubles event, losing the chance to fight for a medal in Nadal's last Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.215680251382653e-28, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 38-year-old already has gold medals in both singles and doubles, and he was hoping to add to his collection one last time.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal's future now remains uncertain.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.215680251382653e-28, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He previously said he would comment on his career plans after the Olympicsbut still had no idea as recently as Monday.\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it may have been the last time fans saw him on Court Philippe-Chatrier at Stade Roland Garros as he and Alcaraz were ousted by No.\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.880168572460112e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"4 seeds Austin Krajicek and Rajeev Ram 6-2 6-4.\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Austin Krajicek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rajeev Ram\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans were by far the toughest opponents that 'Nadalcaraz' had faced.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2403729741262861e-20, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both have reached No.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 in the world and Ram has four men's doubles Grand Slam titles, while Krajicek won the French Open doubles last year.\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their experience was clear to see as Nadal and Alcaraz struggled to get past them, with the fourth seeds proving to be like brick walls up at the net.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.215680251382653e-28, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.880168572460112e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Krajicek and Ram immediately drew first blood, breaking in the opening game, and it made the first set an uphill battle for the Spaniards.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.9910669277098859, \"rank\": 0.008916750068140364, \"text\": \"Spaniards\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They constantly seemed under pressure on serve.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Alcaraz crumbled in a lengthy game while serving at 2-4, giving away another break on a double fault.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.880168572460112e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spanish duo blew their first break point and Ram served out the first set in 43 minutes.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1284, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9432064839579969, \"rank\": 0.05299860678308919, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal and Alcaraz raised their level in the second set but it still wasn't enough to trouble either of the Americans in their service games.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.880168572460112e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the fans in the biggest showcourt at Stade Roland Garros were clearly on their side, booing anyone who dared to cheer for the USA.\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9936605448939066, \"rank\": 0.0062915403455819155, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Alcaraz was suddenly in more trouble, facing a triple break point on his serve.\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.880168572460112e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And there was drama when a forehand winner from the Americans was called out, only for the chair umpire to come down and overrule it.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Boos rang out around Chatrier as the Spaniard tried to plead their case but they had no luck and Krajicek and Ram got the break.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1906, \"end\": 1914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.9826829866130491, \"rank\": 0.017598254764734842, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Andy Murray backed to copy Roger Federer as Olympics rival eager to retire Brit  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2007, \"end\": 2018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.977145316508415e-78, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2034, \"end\": 2047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roger Federer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy      Nadal's dream of one last Olympic medal was slipping through his fingers as Ram put them within a game of taking the match and reaching the semi-final, where even the losers get the chance to compete for bronze.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 38-year-old served to stay in the match and kept them alive.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The spectators were on their feet when Krajicek stepped up to serve for the match and hit a double fault as chants of \\\"ole\\\" reverberated off the closed roof.\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Suddenly, the Spaniards had a lifeline.\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2700, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.9910669277098859, \"rank\": 0.008916750068140364, \"text\": \"Spaniards\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz roared as he fired down a return winner to give them two break points and the chants in Chatrier were deafening.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.880168572460112e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It turned into a rollercoaster.\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Krajicek saved both before an error gave Nadalcaraz one more chance.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair from the USA finally got to match point but they could not handle Nadal's power and netted the ball.\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2967, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9936605448939066, \"rank\": 0.0062915403455819155, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3024, \"end\": 3029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.215680251382653e-28, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match could not finish without more dramatics.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On their second match point, Krajicek hit a serve that had to be confirmed by the umpire.\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal and Alcaraz huddled over as their dream hung in the balance.\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3211, \"end\": 3218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.880168572460112e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Miriam Blay showed a flat hand, confirming it was in, and there was a relatively muted response from the crowd before the multi-Grand Slam singles champions received a standing ovation.\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3268, \"end\": 3274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miriam\", \"score\": 0.9999994065617044, \"rank\": 5.934379318617081e-07, \"text\": \"Miriam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miriam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miriam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Olympics drop Murray hint as tennis star sent into retirement in sorry style  Do not miss:Nick Kyrgios calls for major Olympics tennis change in 'better drama' plea  Do not miss:Stefanos Tsitsipas fires locker room warning to Djokovic ahead of Olympics clash  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3481, \"end\": 3487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.693409051516092e-51, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3557, \"end\": 3569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Kyrgios\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nick Kyrgios\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Kyrgios\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Kyrgios\"}, {\"begin\": 3693, \"end\": 3701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.19711974936186e-19, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    It's not known whether the doubles match will prove to be the last of Nadal's career.\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 4058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4043, \"end\": 4048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.215680251382653e-28, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-time Grand Slam champion has repeated on several occasions that he will make a decision about his future and whether he will retire once the Olympics is over, though he has committed to playing in September's Laver Cup.\", \"from\": 4059, \"to\": 4285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, afterlosing to long-time rival Novak Djokovic in the singles on Monday, it sounded like he still had not come to a conclusion.\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4323, \"end\": 4337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I come here, I try my best, I play and when I decide to stop playing or when I decide to keep going, I will let you know,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4419, \"to\": 4551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know, I just try my best every single day, trying to enjoy a thing that I have been enjoying for so much time.\", \"from\": 4553, \"to\": 4673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been suffering a lot of injuries the last two years so if I feel that I am not competitive enough to keep going or physically I am not ready enough to keep going, I will stop and I will let you know.\", \"from\": 4674, \"to\": 4880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I mean, I do not think every day about if I am retiring or not.\\\"\", \"from\": 4881, \"to\": 4949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 4951, \"to\": 5120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5088, \"end\": 5101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.204625503280828e-26, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5137, \"end\": 5150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.204625503280828e-26, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", 